trans-unit.source: Isolates into a separate class methods that are used by the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager"></xref> control and can be overridden by developers who extend the control, but are rarely needed by page developers.
trans-unit.target: Isolerar i en separat klass-metoder som används av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager"> </xref> styr och kan åsidosättas med utvecklare som utöka kontrollen, men sällan behövs av sidan utvecklare.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> class is the largest class in the Web Parts control set.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>klass är den största klassen i uppsättningen av kontrollen webbdelar.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: It is also among the most important Web Parts classes because it is used on every Web page that contains Web Parts controls, and it coordinates and manages all Web Parts controls on a page.
trans-unit.target: Det är också bland de viktigaste webbdelar klasserna eftersom den används på varje webbsida som innehåller webbdelar kontroller, och det samordnar och hanterar alla webbdelar kontroller på en sida.

trans-unit.source: Because the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> class is used so frequently, and because it contains so many exposed methods, some methods needed mostly by control developers who are extending the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control are contained in the WebPartManagerInternals class.
trans-unit.target: Eftersom den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>klassen används så ofta och eftersom den innehåller så många exponerade metoder några metoder krävs oftast av kontrollen utvecklare som utökar <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollen finns i klassen WebPartManagerInternals.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: This isolation of less-used methods into the WebPartManagerInternals class simplifies the API of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> class, and the isolated methods do not appear on the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> object in IntelliSense.
trans-unit.target: Denna isolering av används mindre metoder i klassen WebPartManagerInternals förenklar API i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>klass och isolerade metoder visas inte på den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>objekt i IntelliSense.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: Developers who use the WebPartManagerInternals class are likely to have scenarios where they need to inherit from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control and customize it extensively.
trans-unit.target: Utvecklare som använder klassen WebPartManagerInternals sannolikt har scenarier där de behöver för att ärva från den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>styra och anpassa den omfattande.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: For example, if you are building a Web portal application or a packaged set of Web Parts controls with custom display modes, custom zones, custom verbs, custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls, and other extensions of the base Web Parts user interface (UI), in many cases (not all) you will need to override and extend some of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> members.
trans-unit.target: Till exempel om du skapar en portal webbprogram eller en paketerad uppsättning webbdelar kontroller med anpassade visningslägen anpassad zoner, anpassade verb anpassad <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroller och andra tillägg för grundläggande webbdelar användargränssnittet (UI) i många fall (alla) behöver du åsidosätta och utöka några av de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>medlemmar.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: And although the WebPartManagerInternals class is sealed so you cannot inherit from it, your custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> class will likely need to call a number of the WebPartManagerInternals methods in order to manage Web Parts controls on a page.
trans-unit.target: Och även om klassen WebPartManagerInternals är förseglat så du inte kan ärva från den, dina anpassade <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>klassen sannolikt måste anropa ett antal WebPartManagerInternals-metoder för att kunna hantera webbdelar kontroller på en sida.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Like the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> class, the WebPartManagerInternals class provides a server control that has no UI and is never visible on a page.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Ut den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>klass, WebPartManagerInternals-klassen innehåller en serverkontroll som inte har något användargränssnitt och aldrig visas på en sida.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: Unlike <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>, the WebPartManagerInternals class is never declared in the markup of a page; it is strictly a worker object that performs background tasks.
trans-unit.target: Till skillnad från <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>, klassen WebPartManagerInternals aldrig har deklarerats i koden för en sida, det är enbart en worker-objekt som utför bakgrundsaktiviteter.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: The typical way of using it is demonstrated by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> class, which references it by means of the protected <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.Internals%2A> property, and uses the referenced object to call the WebPartManagerInternals methods.
trans-unit.target: Vanliga sätt att använda det framgår av de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>klass som refererar till den med hjälp av den skyddade <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.Internals%2A>egenskap, och använder det refererade objektet för att anropa WebPartManagerInternals-metoder.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.Internals%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartManagerInternals class contains only methods; there are no properties or events.
trans-unit.target: Klassen WebPartManagerInternals innehåller endast metoder. Det finns inga egenskaper eller händelser.

trans-unit.source: All the methods in the class involve managing <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls, or connections between controls.
trans-unit.target: Alla metoder i klassen innebär hantera <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroller eller anslutningar mellan kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: To handle <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls, WebPartManagerInternals includes methods for adding them (<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.AddWebPart%2A>), removing them <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.RemoveWebPart%2A>), handling events <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.CallOnDeleting%2A>), getting or setting details about their relationship to their zone (for example, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.GetZoneID%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.SetZoneIndex%2A>), or setting basic <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control properties (for example, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.SetIsClosed%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.SetHasSharedData%2A>).
trans-unit.target: Att hantera <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroller, WebPartManagerInternals innehåller metoder för att lägga till dem (<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.AddWebPart%2A>), ta bort dem <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.RemoveWebPart%2A>), hantera händelser <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.CallOnDeleting%2A>), hämta eller ange information om deras relation till deras zon (till exempel <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.GetZoneID%2A>och <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.SetZoneIndex%2A>), eller ställer in grundläggande <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollegenskaper (till exempel <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.SetIsClosed%2A>och <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.SetHasSharedData%2A>).</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.SetHasSharedData%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.SetIsClosed%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.SetZoneIndex%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.GetZoneID%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.CallOnDeleting%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.RemoveWebPart%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.AddWebPart%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: To handle connections, WebPartManagerInternals includes methods for deleting them (<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.DeleteConnection%2A>), setting which transformer object to use (<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.SetTransformer%2A>), setting whether a connection is shared and whether it is static (<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.SetIsShared%28System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection%2CSystem.Boolean%29> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.SetIsStatic%28System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection%2CSystem.Boolean%29>), and setting a connection error message to use (<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.SetConnectErrorMessage%2A>).
trans-unit.target: Om du vill hantera anslutningar WebPartManagerInternals innehåller metoder för att ta bort dem (<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.DeleteConnection%2A>), ange vilka objekt som transformatorn ska användas (<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.SetTransformer%2A>), Ställ om en anslutning delas och om det är statiska (<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.SetIsShared%28System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection%2CSystem.Boolean%29> och <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.SetIsStatic%28System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection%2CSystem.Boolean%29>), och ange ett felmeddelande för anslutning för att använda (<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.SetConnectErrorMessage%2A>).</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.SetConnectErrorMessage%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.SetIsStatic%28System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection%2CSystem.Boolean%29> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.SetIsShared%28System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection%2CSystem.Boolean%29> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.SetTransformer%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.DeleteConnection%2A>

trans-unit.target: Anger om den angivna <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection"> </xref> objektet har tagits bort.

trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection"> </xref> som har markerats för borttagning.

trans-unit.source: A Boolean value that indicates whether the connection has been deleted.
trans-unit.target: Ett booleskt värde som anger om anslutningen har tagits bort.

trans-unit.source: Creates an object based on the parameter passed to the method.
trans-unit.target: Skapar ett objekt baserat på den parameter som överförts till metoden.

trans-unit.target: Anger en egenskap som anger att det angivna connection-objektet har tagits bort.

trans-unit.source: The DeleteConnection method is one step in the process of terminating an existing connection between two <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> or other server controls on a Web page.
trans-unit.target: Metoden DeleteConnection är ett steg håller på att avslutas av en befintlig anslutning mellan två <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>eller andra kontroller på en webbsida.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: It sets the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.ConnectionDeleted%2A> property value to `true` to indicate that `connection` is deleted.
trans-unit.target: Anger den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.ConnectionDeleted%2A>egenskapsvärdet till `true` som indikerar att `connection` tas bort.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.ConnectionDeleted%2A>

trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection"> </xref> som har markerats för borttagning.

trans-unit.source: Gets the ID of a zone that contains the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> or server control.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar ID för en zon som innehåller den angivna <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> eller server-kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The GetZoneID method returns the ID of the zone that contains the control referenced by the `webPart` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Metoden GetZoneID returnerar ID för zonen som innehåller kontrollen refererar till den `webPart` parameter.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Zone%2A> property of `webPart` references the actual zone object that contains `webPart`, not the ID of the zone.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Zone%2A>egenskapen för `webPart` refererar till zonen-objekt som innehåller `webPart`, inte ID för zonen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Zone%2A>

trans-unit.source: If `webPart` is currently closed, the value of its <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Zone%2A> property is `null`, and the GetZoneID method will return the ID of the last zone that `webPart` was in prior to being closed.
trans-unit.target: Om `webPart` är stängt, värdet för dess <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Zone%2A>egenskapen är `null`, och metoden GetZoneID returnerar ID för senaste zonen som `webPart` användes innan stängdes.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Zone%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> that resides in a zone.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> som finns i en zon.

trans-unit.source: A string that represents the ID of the zone that contains webPart.
trans-unit.target: En sträng som representerar ID för zonen som innehåller webPart .

trans-unit.target: Belastningarna sparats anger data för en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"> </xref> objekt som deltar i en anslutning mellan kontroller.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> that is used to connect controls.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"> </xref> som används för att ansluta kontroller.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Object> that contains the previously saved state data.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Object>som innehåller data som tidigare sparat läge.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.target: Tar bort en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> eller annan serverkontroll från den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager"> </xref> kontrollsamling av kontroller.

trans-unit.target: Tar bort `webPart` från aktuellt <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollsamling av webbdelar kontroller som det finns för sidan.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> or other server control to be removed.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> eller annan serverkontroll som ska tas bort.

trans-unit.source: Saves state data for a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> object that participates in a connection between controls.
trans-unit.target: Sparar tillstånd data för en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"> </xref> objekt som deltar i en anslutning mellan kontroller.

trans-unit.source: The SaveConfigurationState method saves configuration data that is created when a user configures a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> control on a Web page as part of a connection between controls.
trans-unit.target: Metoden SaveConfigurationState sparar konfigurationsdata som skapas när en användare konfigurerar en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>på en webbsida som en del av en anslutning mellan kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>

trans-unit.source: This configuration data is then reloaded each time the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> control is rendered, by using the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.LoadConfigurationState%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Den här konfigurationsdata läses sedan varje gång den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>kontrollen återges med hjälp av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.LoadConfigurationState%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerInternals.LoadConfigurationState%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> that is used to connect controls.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"> </xref> som används för att ansluta kontroller.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Object> that contains the saved state data.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Object>som innehåller data för sparat tillstånd.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: Establishes an errors message, and causes the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartChrome"></xref> object that is responsible for rendering a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control to render that message rather than the contents of the control.
trans-unit.target: Upprättar en fel-meddelande och gör den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartChrome"> </xref> objekt som är ansvarig för återgivning en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontrollen ska renderas meddelandet i stället för innehållet i kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The SetConnectErrorMessage method allows you to associate an error message with a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control that participates in connections.
trans-unit.target: Metoden SetConnectErrorMessage kan du associera ett felmeddelande med en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll som deltar i anslutningar.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: If an error occurs when another control is forming a connection with the control referenced by the `webPart` parameter, then after the connection process has failed, the error message is displayed in the user interface (UI), rather than the contents of `webPart`.
trans-unit.target: Om ett fel uppstår när en annan kontroll som utgör en anslutning med kontrollen refererar till den `webPart` parameter när anslutningen har misslyckats, ett felmeddelande visas i användargränssnittet (UI) i stället för innehållet i `webPart`.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartChrome> object associated with `webPart` renders the error message in its <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartChrome.RenderPartContents%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartChrome>som är associerat med `webPart` återgivningar felmeddelandet i dess <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartChrome.RenderPartContents%2A>metod.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartChrome.RenderPartContents%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartChrome>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> that participates in a connection with another control.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> som deltar i en anslutning med en annan kontroll.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the text of the error message.
trans-unit.target: En sträng som innehåller text i felmeddelandet.

trans-unit.source: Sets a property on a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> or other server control indicating whether the control has shared personalization data.
trans-unit.target: Anger en egenskap för en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> eller andra Serverkontrollen som anger om kontrollen har delat anpassningsdata.

trans-unit.source: The SetHasSharedData method indicates whether `webPart` has shared personalization data.
trans-unit.target: Metoden SetHasSharedData anger om `webPart` har delat anpassningsdata.

trans-unit.source: The value of the `hasSharedData` parameter that is passed into the method is assigned to the `webPart` control's <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.HasSharedData%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Värdet för den `hasSharedData` parameter som överförs till metoden som har tilldelats den `webPart` kontrollens <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.HasSharedData%2A>egenskap.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.HasSharedData%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> or other server control that can have shared personalization data.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> eller andra Serverkontrollen som kan ha delad anpassningsdata.

trans-unit.source: A Boolean value that indicates whether `webPart` has shared data.
trans-unit.target: Ett booleskt värde som anger om `webPart` har delade data.

trans-unit.source: Sets a property on a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> or other server control indicating whether the control has user personalization data.
trans-unit.target: Anger en egenskap för en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> eller andra Serverkontrollen som anger om kontrollen har anpassningsdata för användaren.

trans-unit.source: The SetHasUserData method indicates whether `webPart` has individual user personalization data, as opposed to shared data.
trans-unit.target: Metoden SetHasUserData anger om `webPart` har anpassningsdata för enskilda användare, till skillnad från delade data.

trans-unit.source: The method assigns the value of the `hasUserData` parameter to the `webPart` control's <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.HasUserData%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Metoden tilldelas värdet i den `hasUserData` parametern till den `webPart` kontrollens <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.HasUserData%2A>egenskap.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.HasUserData%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> or other server control that can have user personalization data.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> eller annan serverkontroll som kan ha anpassningsdata för användaren.

trans-unit.source: A Boolean value that indicates whether `webPart` has shared data.
trans-unit.target: Ett booleskt värde som anger om `webPart` har delade data.

trans-unit.source: Sets the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsClosed*> property of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Anger den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsClosed*>-egenskapen för en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsClosed*>

trans-unit.source: The SetIsClosed method sets the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsClosed%2A> property of `webPart`.
trans-unit.target: SetIsClosed metoden anger den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsClosed%2A>egenskapen för `webPart`.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsClosed%2A>

trans-unit.source: This method does not actually close `webPart`; it only sets the property that indicates whether `webPart` is closed.
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden stängs faktiskt inte `webPart`; endast anger den egenskap som anger om `webPart` är stängd.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> for which this method sets the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsClosed*> property.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> för den här metoden anger det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsClosed*>egenskap.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsClosed*>

trans-unit.source: A Boolean value that indicates whether a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> is closed on a page.
trans-unit.target: Ett booleskt värde som anger om en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> har stängts på en sida.

trans-unit.source: Sets the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsShared*> property of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Anger den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsShared*>-egenskapen för en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsShared*>

trans-unit.source: The SetIsShared method does not actually cause the control referenced by the `webPart` parameter to be shared; it only sets the property that indicates whether `webPart` is currently shared.
trans-unit.target: Metoden SetIsShared inte faktiskt orsakar kontrollen refererar till den `webPart` parameter som ska delas; endast anger den egenskap som anger om `webPart` delas.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> for which this method sets the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsShared*> property.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> för den här metoden anger det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsShared*>egenskap.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsShared*>

trans-unit.source: A Boolean value that indicates whether `webPart` is shared.
trans-unit.target: Ett booleskt värde som anger om `webPart` delas.

trans-unit.source: Sets the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection.IsShared*> property of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Anger den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection.IsShared*>-egenskapen för en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection"> </xref> objekt.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection.IsShared*>

trans-unit.source: The SetIsShared method does not actually cause the control referenced by the `connection` parameter to be shared; it only sets the property that indicates whether `connection` is currently shared.
trans-unit.target: Metoden SetIsShared inte faktiskt orsakar kontrollen refererar till den `connection` parameter som ska delas; endast anger den egenskap som anger om `connection` delas.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection"></xref> between two <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection"> </xref> mellan två <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroller.

trans-unit.source: A Boolean value that indicates whether `connection` is shared.
trans-unit.target: Ett booleskt värde som anger om `connection` delas.

trans-unit.source: Sets the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsStandalone*> property of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Anger den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsStandalone*>-egenskapen för en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsStandalone*>

trans-unit.source: The SetIsStandalone method sets the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsStandalone%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: SetIsStandalone metoden anger det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsStandalone%2A>egenskap.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsStandalone%2A>

trans-unit.source: When this property is set to `true` on a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control, it means that the control is not contained within a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> zone.
trans-unit.target: När den här egenskapen har angetts `true` på en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll, innebär det att kontrollen inte finns i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase>zon.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> for which this method sets the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsStandalone*> property.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> för den här metoden anger det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsStandalone*>egenskap.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsStandalone*>

trans-unit.source: A Boolean value that indicates whether `webPart` is a standalone control.
trans-unit.target: Ett booleskt värde som anger om `webPart` är en fristående kontroll.

trans-unit.source: Sets the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsStatic*> property of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Anger den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsStatic*>-egenskapen för en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsStatic*>

trans-unit.source: The SetIsStatic method is used to set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsStatic%2A> property value of the control referenced by the `webPart` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Metoden SetIsStatic används för att ange den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsStatic%2A>-värdet för den kontroll som refererar till den `webPart` parameter.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.IsStatic%2A>

trans-unit.source: If `webPart` is declared within a zone in the markup of a Web page, this method sets the property value to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Om `webPart` har deklarerats inom en zon i koden för en webbsida, den här metoden egenskapsvärdet till `true`.

trans-unit.source: If `webPart` is added to a page programmatically, or by a user through the Web Parts user interface (UI), then this method sets the property value to `false`.
trans-unit.target: Om `webPart` läggs till en sida programmässigt eller av en användare via webbdelar användargränssnittet (UI) och sedan på den här metoden anger egenskapens värde till `false`.

trans-unit.source: The control for which the property value is being set.
trans-unit.target: Den kontroll som egenskapsvärdet anges.

trans-unit.source: A Boolean value that indicates whether `webPart` is static.
trans-unit.target: Ett booleskt värde som anger om `webPart` är statisk.

trans-unit.source: Sets the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection.IsStatic*> property of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Anger den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection.IsStatic*>-egenskapen för en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection"> </xref> objekt.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection.IsStatic*>

trans-unit.source: The SetIsStatic method is used to set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection.IsStatic%2A> property value of the connection referenced by the `connection` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Metoden SetIsStatic används för att ange den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection.IsStatic%2A>-värdet för den anslutning som refererar till den `connection` parameter.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection.IsStatic%2A>

trans-unit.source: If `connection` is declared in the markup of a Web page, this method sets the property value to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Om `connection` är deklarerad i koden för en webbsida, den här metoden egenskapsvärdet till `true`.

trans-unit.source: If `connection` is added to a page programmatically, or by a user through the Web Parts user interface (UI), then this method sets the property value to `false`.
trans-unit.target: Om `connection` läggs till en sida programmässigt eller av en användare via webbdelar användargränssnittet (UI) och sedan på den här metoden anger egenskapens värde till `false`.

trans-unit.source: The connection for which the property value is being set.
trans-unit.target: Anslutningen som egenskapens värde anges.

trans-unit.source: A Boolean value that indicates whether `connection` is static.
trans-unit.target: Ett booleskt värde som anger om `connection` är statisk.

trans-unit.source: Assigns a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> object to be used in a connection between two server controls.
trans-unit.target: Tilldelar en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"> </xref> objekt som ska användas i en anslutning mellan två server-kontroller.

trans-unit.source: When a connection between two server controls requires a transformer so that the consumer control can interpret data from the provider control, the SetTransformer method is called to supply a specific <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> object to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection> object.
trans-unit.target: När en anslutning mellan två serverkontroller kräver en transformator så att konsumenten kontrollen kan tolka data från providern kontrollen, SetTransformer-metoden anropas för att ange en specifik <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>objekt i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection>objekt.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>

trans-unit.source: If the connection already has a transformer assigned to it, the object referenced by the `transformer` parameter overrides the existing one; otherwise, the object referenced in the `transformer` parameter is used.
trans-unit.target: Om anslutningen redan har en transformator tilldelats, objektet refererar till den `transformer` parametern åsidosätter befintlig; annars refererar till objektet i den `transformer` parametern används.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control uses the SetTransformer method whenever you call the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.ConnectWebParts%2A> method to establish a connection that requires a transformer.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollen använder metoden SetTransformer när du anropar den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.ConnectWebParts%2A>metod för att upprätta en anslutning som kräver en transformator.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.ConnectWebParts%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection"></xref> that creates a connection between server controls.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection"> </xref> som skapar en anslutning mellan kontroller.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> to be used with `connection`.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"> </xref> som ska användas med `connection`.

trans-unit.source: Sets a property that enables a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> or server control to keep the ID of the containing zone.
trans-unit.target: Anger en egenskap som gör att en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> eller server-kontroll att hålla ID för den överordnade zonen.

trans-unit.source: This method is called by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control when a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control is being added to a zone.
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden anropas av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>styra när en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll läggs till i en zon.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control tracks the ID for the zone it belongs to, and this method sets the property that keeps the ID value.
trans-unit.target: Varje <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll spårar ID för det hör till zonen och den här metoden anger den egenskap som bevarar ID-värde.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> whose `zoneID` property value is being set.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> vars `zoneID` egenskapsvärde anges.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the ID of the zone that `webPart` belongs to.
trans-unit.target: En sträng som innehåller ID för zonen som `webPart` tillhör.

trans-unit.source: Sets the index of the specified control within its zone relative to the other <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> controls within the zone.
trans-unit.target: Anger indexet för den angivna kontrollen inom zonen i förhållande till den andra <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroller inom zonen.

trans-unit.source: The SetZoneIndex method determines the ordinal position that `webPart` occupies in its zone, relative to other server controls in the zone.
trans-unit.target: Metoden SetZoneIndex anger ordningstalet position som `webPart` upptar i zonen, i förhållande till andra kontroller i zonen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control for which the method sets a zone index.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroll som metoden anger Zonindex för en.

trans-unit.source: The index of `webPart` within its zone relative to other controls in the zone.
trans-unit.target: Index för `webPart` inom zonen i förhållande till andra kontroller i zonen.
